      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for primary QoI (hemolysis index) with GCI < 5% on fine grid.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on FDA pump geometry. GCI for normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) on fine mesh is 3.2%, satisfying the < 5% acceptance criterion."
